nced%20the%20first%20cohort%20of%20Hawaii's%20student-loan%20repayment%20program%20for%20healthcare%20workers.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAudrey%20McAvoy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHawaii%20announced%20the%20first%20recipients%20of%20a%20student-loan%20repayment%20program%20for%20healthcare%20workers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENearly%20500%20workers%20will%20get%20up%20to%20%24100%2C000%20in%20debt%20relief%20if%20they%20work%20in%20the%20state%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20among%20a%20number%20of%20state-level%20efforts%20to%20get%20student-debt%20relief%20to%20borrowers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20healthcare%20workers%20in%20Hawaii%20might%20be%20on%20track%20for%20six%20figures%20in%20student-loan%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20days%20before%20Christmas%2C%20Hawaii%20Gov.%20Josh%20Green%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgovernor.hawaii.gov%2Ffeatured%2Fhelping-hundreds-of-healthcare-professionals-stay-in-hawai%25CA%25BBi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20492%20healthcare%20workers%20had%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20state's%20first%20cohort%20of%20the%20Hawaii%20Healthcare%20Education%20Loan%20Repayment%20Program%2C%20or%20HELP%20program.%20The%20program%20promises%20to%20repay%20up%20to%20%24100%2C000%20of%20the%20worker's%20student%20loans%20%E2%80%94%20%2450%2C000%20per%20year%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20they%20commit%20to%20working%20full-time%20for%20two%20years%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20so%20rewarding%20to%20see%20this%20program%20come%20to%20fruition%2C%20as%20it%20was%20this%20type%20of%20assistance%20that%20first%20brought%20me%20to%20Hawai'i%20so%20many%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%2C%20a%20physician%20himself%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20firsthand%20how%20desperately%20needed%20medical%20care%20is%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20areas%20of%20the%20islands%20and%20for%20underserved%20populations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BHELP%20will%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20great%20start%20toward%20decreasing%20our%20long-standing%20and%20challenging%20shortage%20of%20healthcare%20professionals%20across%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20HELP's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahec.hawaii.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F16%2F2021%2F12%2FFinal-Hawaii-HELP-Program-Overview-1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efact%20sheet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20two-year%20commitment%20is%20required%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20program%2C%20and%20continuation%20is%20then%20evaluated%20on%20a%20year-by-year%20basis.%20The%20worker%20must%20be%20licensed%20in%20Hawaii%20to%20qualify%2C%20and%20they%20must%20take%20a%20minimum%2030%25%20of%20patience%20on%20public%20insurance.%20Those%20who%20wish%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20next%20cohort%20can%20do%20so%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahec.hawaii.edu%2Fhawai%25CA%25BBi-help%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20program%20is%20funded%20with%20%2430%20million%20from%20the%20Hawaii%20state%20legislature%20and%20an%20additional%20%245%20million%20from%20the%20CEO%20of%20Salesforce%2C%20Mark%20Benioff%2C%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Lynne%20Benioff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHawaii's%20program%20is%20just%20one%20of%20a%20number%20of%20efforts%20on%20the%20state%20level%20to%20get%20student-debt%20relief%20to%20borrowers.%20In%20Maine%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20state's%20lawmakers%20in%202022%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaine-willl-pay-student-loan-debt-if-you-buy-house-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewere%20proposing%20up%20to%20%2440%2C000%20in%20debt%20relief%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20efforts%20come%20as%20the%20fate%20of%20broader%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20remains%20uncertain%20at%20the%20federal%20level.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estruck%20down%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20first%20attempt%20at%20broad%20student-loan%20forgiveness%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20Education%20Department%20announced%20the%20same%20day%20that%20it%20would%20be%20pursuing%20a%20narrower%20scale%20of%20relief%20using%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20of%201965.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20department%20recently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-student-loan-borrowers-will-get-debt-cancellation-biden-hardship-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econcluded%20negotiations%20with%20stakeholders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20what%20the%20text%20of%20the%20relief%20should%20look%20like%2C%20and%20the%20public%20can%20expect%20an%20opportunity%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20proposals%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%2C%20millions%20of%20federal%20borrowers%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-repayment-issues-debt-relief-broken-industry-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereturn%20to%20repayment%20after%20an%20over-three-year%20pause%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20With%20the%20burden%20of%20an%20additional%20monthly%20bill%2C%20many%20are%20waiting%20to%20see%20when%2C%20or%20if%2C%20they%20will%20see%20a%20reduction%20in%20their%20balances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20targeted%20programs%2C%20like%20the%20one%20Hawaii%20is%20implementing%20for%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20might%20help.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20one%20of%20the%20key%20lessons%20we've%20learned%20over%20the%20years%20is%20we%20simply%20don't%20have%20enough%20healthcare%20providers%20in%20the%20places%20we%20need%20the%20most%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspectrumlocalnews.com%2Fhi%2Fhawaii%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F12%2F24%2Fnearly-500-health-professionals-selected-for-loan-forgiveness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20a%20December%2022%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20our%20team%20has%20been%20thinking%20about%20this%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-hawaii-healthcare-repayment-debt-relief-help-program-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703546134000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6589fc2bec62ab5daf7e9e2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-hawaii-healthcare-repayment-debt-relief-help-program-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Hawaii%20student-loan%20repayment%20program%20just%20selected%20492%20healthcare%20workers%20for%20debt%20relief%20as%20long%20as%20they%20work%20in%20the%20state%20for%20two%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-hawaii-healthcare-repayment-debt-relief-help-program-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%