report%3C%2Fa%3E%20detailed%20the%20close%20relationship%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%20maintains%20with%20his%20former%20clerks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he's%20even%20gotten%20some%20gifts%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F12%2F24%2Fus%2Fclarence-thomas-supreme-court-clerks.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Thomas%20has%20built%20a%20tight-knit%20network%20of%20his%20former%20clerks%2C%20and%20his%20continued%20relationships%20with%20them%20have%20kept%20them%20loyal%2C%20defending%20him%20as%20he%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20over%20the%20past%20year%20over%20his%20ties%20to%20billionaires%20and%20gifts%20he's%20failed%20to%20disclose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Thomas%20has%20stayed%20in%20touch%20with%20his%20clerks%20over%20the%20years%20by%20arranging%20monthly%20lunches%20at%20Morton's%20The%20Steakhouse%20or%20another%20restaurant%2C%20along%20with%20trips%20to%20Gettysburg's%20Civil%20War%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20favors%20have%20not%20gone%20unreturned.%20For%20example%2C%20one%20of%20Thomas'%20former%20clerks%20purchased%20a%20taxidermy%20lobster%20in%201998%20from%20a%20Virginia%20man%20whose%20summer%20home%20had%20been%20previously%20been%20robbed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20lobster%20in%20question%20was%20stolen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20had%20rejected%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20man%20who%20robbed%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20reported%20that%20the%20former%20clerk%20procured%20and%20gifted%20Thomas%20the%20stuffed%20lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20other%20clerks%20have%20also%20presented%20Thomas%20with%20gifts%20over%20the%20years%20as%20tokens%20of%20loyalty%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-purchased-luxury-rv-with-help-of-healthcare-executive-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%