0risk%20of%20penis%20injury%20during%20Christmas%2C%20new%20research%20suggests.%3Cp%3EBusiness%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-have-best-better-sex-2017-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIntense%20sex%20%3C%2Fa%3Eduring%20Christmas%20may%20be%20ending%20in%20embarrassing%20trips%20to%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20research%20suggests%20there's%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20getting%20a%20penile%20fracture%20during%20Christmas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20may%20be%20because%20holiday%20spirit%20may%20be%20leading%20to%20more%20dangerous%2C%20intense%20sex%2C%20per%20the%20research.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChristmas%20might%20be%20making%20us%20friskier%2C%20leading%20to%20intense%20sex%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20embarrassing%20trips%20to%20the%20emergency%20room%2C%20new%20research%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbjui-journals.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fepdf%2F10.1111%2Fbju.16216%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20British%20Journal%20of%20Urology%20this%20year%2C%20researchers%20analyzed%203%2C421%20cases%20of%20men%20who%20went%20to%20the%20hospital%20because%20of%20a%20penile%20fracture%20between%202005%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20define%20a%20penile%20fracture%20%E2%80%94%20which%20they%20say%20often%20occurs%20during%20rowdy%20sexual%20intercourse%20%E2%80%94%20as%20an%20audible%20crack%20in%20the%20penis%2C%20followed%20by%20severe%20pain%2C%20swelling%2C%20and%20bruising%20in%20the%20genital%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20injury%20tends%20to%20occur%20during%20wild%20sex%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20in%20positions%20where%20you're%20not%20in%20direct%20eye%20contact%20%5Bwith%20your%20partner%5D%2C%20such%20as%20the%20reverse%20cowgirl%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr.%20Nikolaos%20Pyrgides%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lead%20resea