20recent%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20vessels%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%2C%20the%20Navy%20has%20deployed%20warships%20INS%20Mormugao%2C%20INS%20Kochi%20and%20INS%20Kolkata%20to%20maintain%20a%20deterrent%20presence%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%20Long-range%20maritime%20reconnaissance%20aircraft%20P8Is%20are%20being%20regularly%20tasked%20to%20maintain%20domain%20awareness%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20claimed%20the%20tanker%20ship%20was%20targeted%20by%20a%20drone%20%26quot%3Bfired%20from%20Iran.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Pentagon%20openly%20accused%20Iran%20of%20directly%20targeting%20ships%20since%20the%20start%20of%20Israel's%20war%20on%20Hamas%2C%20which%20is%20backed%20by%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20and%20the%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20swung%20into%20action%20by%20deploying%20their%20assets%20including%20a%20warship%20and%20maritime%20patrol%20aircraft%20on%20Saturday%20soon%20after%20the%20UK%20Maritime%20Trade%20Operations%2C%20or%20UKMTO%2C%20reported%20the%20drone%20attack%20on%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UKMTO%20is%20a%20British%20military%20organisation%20that%20provides%20maritime%20security%20information%20and%20largely%20acts%20as%20the%20primary%20point%20of%20contact%20for%20merchant%20vessels%20involved%20in%20maritime%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vessel%20was%20reportedly%20carrying%20crude%20oil%20to%20the%20New%20Mangalore%20port%20from%20the%20Al%20Jubail%20port%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20MV%20Chem%20Pluto%20has%20been%20cleared%20for%20further%20operation%20by%20its%20company-in-charge%20at%20Mumbai.%20The%20ship%20is%20scheduled%20to%20undergo%20mandatory%20checks%20by%20the%20various%20inspecting%20authorities%20before%20undertaking%20Ship%20to%20Ship%20(STS)%20transfer%20of%20cargo.%20This%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20docking%20and%20repairs%20of%20the%20damaged%20portion%20of%20MV%20Chem%20Pluto.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703525880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fkrf3dvm_mv-chem-pluto_625x300_25_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmerchant-ship-mv-chem-pluto-was-struck-by-drone-400-km-west-of-indian-coastline-confirms-navy-analysis-4741241%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Merchant%20ship%20MV%20Chem%20Pluto%20was%20struck%20by%20drone%20400%20km%20west%20of%20Indian%20coastline%2C%20confirms%20Navy%20analysis%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmerchant-ship-mv-chem-pluto-was-struck-by-drone-400-km-west-of-indian-coastline-confirms-navy-analysis-4741241%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmerchant-ship-mv-chem-pluto-was-struck-by-drone-400-km-west-of-indian-coastline-confirms-navy-analysis-4741241%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmerchant-ship-mv-chem-pluto-was-struck-by-drone-400-km-west-of-indian-coastline-confirms-navy-analysis-4741241%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20strike%20in%20Syria%20kills%20Iranian%20commander%2C%20Iran%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703525808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F4082%2Fproduction%2F_132141561_gettyimages-1085741272.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67820538%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seyyed%20Razi%20Mousavi%2C%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Guards%2C%20died%20in%20an%20Israeli%20strike%2C%20Iran%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67820538%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67820538.amp%22%2C%22ampUr