0Sri%20Akal%20Takht%20Sahib%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Badal%20also%20claimed%20the%20Punjab%20government%20is%20being%20run%20by%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20%26quot%3BThey%20(AAP)%20are%20looting%20Punjab%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Punjab%2C%20not%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Akali%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20stormed%20to%20power%20in%20Punjab%20with%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20the%202022%20state%20polls%2C%20bagging%2092%20seats%20in%20the%20117-member%20Assembly%20and%20trouncing%20the%20Congress%20that%20managed%20to%20win%2018%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2061-year-old%20leader%20today%20met%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Sikh%20Sangat%20of%20Sri%20Patna%20Sahib%20(Bihar)%20and%20Mumbai%20(Maharashtra)%20at%20the%20party's%20Delhi%20State%20unit%20president%20S%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Sarna's%20residence.%20He%20announced%20that%20%26quot%3BShiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20will%20establish%20party%20units%20in%20all%20States%20having%20Sikh%20population%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20the%20community%20to%20stay%20united%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20to%20all%20of%20you%20not%20to%20be%20divided%20and%20remain%20united...Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20will%20establish%20party%20units%20in%20all%20the%20states...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20also%20witnessed%20veteran%20Akali%20leader%20S%20Manjit%20Singh%20GK%20rejoining%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20along%20with%20his%20entire%20Jago%20party%20team.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20this%20unity%20will%20not%20only%20strengthen%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%20but%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20resolution%20of%20all%20our%20pending%20demands%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Badal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20part%20of%20a%20process%20to%20effect%20Panthic%20unity%20in%20the%20Sikh%20quom.%20The%20community%20is%20facing%20various%20challenges%20a