for-first-test-4738487%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fhope-he-proves-me-wrong-sunil-gavaskar-doubts-india-stars-preparedness-for-first-test-4738487%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20Was%20Mutual%20Decision%26quot%3B%3A%20Sharad%20Pawar%20vs%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Over%201978%20%26quot%3BRebellion%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%20on%20Monday%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20reference%20of%20the%201978%20move%20by%20the%20former%20against%20then%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Vasantdada%20Patil%20and%20said%20that%20was%20not%20a%20rebellion%20but%20a%20decision%20taken%20after%20mutual%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201978%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20government%20with%2040%20MLAs%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Patil%20dispensation.%20The%20NCP%20supremo%2C%20on%20July%2018%20that%20year%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20chief%20minister.%20He%20was%20the%20youngest%20on%20the%20post%20at%2038.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20while%20speaking%20in%20Baramati%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20split%20the%20NCP%20on%20July%202%20and%20joined%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%2C%20had%20taken%20a%20swipe%20at%20Sharad%20Pawar%20by%20saying%20his%20stand%20came%20after%20crossing%2060%20while%20some%20went%20down%20that%20path%20at%20the%20age%20of%2038.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20had%20further%20claimed%20Yashwantrao%20Chavan%20had%20opposed%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20move%20as%20a%20leader%20like%20Vasantdada%20Patil%20was%20pushed%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVasantdada%20was%20a%20good%20leader%20but%20he%20was%20kept%20aside%20and%20the%20experiment%20with%20Janata%20Party%20was%20done.%20So%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20nobody%20in%20the%20past%20took%20the%20kind%20of%20step%20that%20I%20took.%20I%20took%20the%20decision%20after%20crossing%2060%2C%20so%20everyone%20needs%20to%20understand%20my%20stand%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajit%20Pawar%20had%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20our%20times%2C%20there%20was%20no%20rebellion.%20We%20used%20to%20sit%20and%20take%20decisions.%20So%20there%20was%20no%20such%20thing%20(rebellion).%20It%20was%20a%20mutual%20decision%20so%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20anyone%20complaining.%26quot%3B%20Queried%20about%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance)%20not%20having%20a%20prime%20ministerial%20face%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%20even%20in%20the%201977%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20(post%20Emergency)%20no%20one%20was%20projected%20as%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20polls%2C%20Moraraji%20Desai%20was%20made%20PM.%20There%20are%20no%20consequences%20if%20a%20face%20is%20not%20projected.%20If%20people%20are%20in%20the%20mood%20for%20change%2C%20they%20will%20take%20a%20call%20to%20bring%20about%20that%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20that%20a%20poll%20survey%20had%20given%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20an%20edge%20over%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%20the%202024%20LS%20polls%2C%20he%20said%20surveys%20are%20just%20indications%20and%20one%20should%20not%20jump%20to%20conclusions%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20such%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQueried%20about%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%20chief%20Prakash%20Ambedkar%20stating%20that%20his%20outfit%20could%20fight%20all%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%20if%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20does%20not%20materialise%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%20all%20political%20groups%20have%20the%20right%20to%20take%20their%20own%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20had%20told%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20in%20a%20meeting%20held%20in%20Delhi%2C%20to%20take%20Ambedkar%20along%2C%20adding%20that%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20had%20also%20contacted%20the%20VBA%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20welcome%20the%20move%20by%20Ambedkar%20and%20our%20colleagues%20to%20work%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NCP%20founder%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20issues%20related%20to%20ethanol%2C%20Pawar%20said%20%26quot%3Bthis%20year%20something%20is%20lacking%20in%20the%20Centre's%20ethanol%20policy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVehicles%20are%20increasing%20in%20the%20country%20and%20crude%20oil%20is%20being%20imported%2C%20while%20countries%20like%20America%20and%20Brazil%20are%20mixing%20ethanol%20and%20fuel%20on%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20do%20something%20similar%2C%20we%20encouraged%20the%20production%20of%20ethanol%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20This%20year%2C%20there%20is%20something%20lacking%20in%20the%20ethanol%20policy%20of%20the%20Centre.%20The%20Centre%20has%20solved%20some%20issues%2C%20but%20some%20big%20aspects%20remain%20unsolved.%20I%20have%20written%20about%20these%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20(Union%20minister)%20Amit%20Shah.%20We%20expect%20a%20positive%20outcome%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703514840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Flrogfps4_ajit-pawar-sharad-pawar-pti-_625x300_26_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-takes-swipe-at-ajit-pawar-says-1978-move-was-not-a-rebellion-4740212%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NCP%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%20on%20Monday%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20reference%20of%20the%201978%20move%20by%20the%20former%20against%20then%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Vasantdada%2