dec%2F23%2Fairbus-atlantic-staff-christmas-dinner-gastroenteritis-outbreak%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EGuardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20lavish%20gourmet%20spread%20featured%20foie%20gras%2C%20scallops%2C%20lobster%2C%20and%20beef%20tenderloin%2C%20capped%20off%20with%20desserts%20like%20ice-cream%20logs%20and%20hazelnut-chocolate%20mousse%20%E2%80%93%20all%20for%20only%20about%20%2416%20per%20person.%20However%2C%20within%2024%20to%2048%20hours%20after%20the%20dinner%2C%20hundreds%20of%20people%20showed%20''clinical%20signs%20of%20vomiting%20and%2For%20diarrhea.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20European%20aeronautics%20company%20told%20CNN%20that%20the%20Airbus%20Atlantic%20employees%20''were%20taken%20ill%20after%20contracting%20a%20food-borne%20illness%20after%20eating%20the%20company-organized%20Christmas%20lunch.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance's%20health%20agency%2C%20Agence%20Regionale%20de%20Sant%20(ARS)%2C%20has%20launched%20an%20investigation%20to%20ascertain%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20mass%20food%20poisoning.%C2%A0Health%20officials%20are%20investigating%20whether%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20illness%20was%20a%20bacterium%20in%20the%20food%20or%20a%20very%20contagious%20gastroenteritis%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''This%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20isolated%20event%20and%20all%20employees%20are%20recovering%20well.%C2%A0The%20health%20of%20our%20employees%20remains%20our%20primary%20concern%20and%20we%20are%20fully%20cooperating%20with%20the%20ARS%20health%20agency%20to%20identify%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20illness%20and%20ensure%20this%20cannot%20happen%20again%20in%20the%20future%2C''%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20company%20said.%C2%A0The%20spokesman%20added%20no%20one%20had%20become%20''seriously%20ill.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20affected%20employee%20said%20that%20she%20had%20colic%20and%20headaches%20worse%20than%20giving%20birth.%C2%A0One%20employee%20named%20only%20as%20Nolwenn%20told%20the%20Ouest-France%20newspaper%3A%20''I%20had%20colic%20and%20headaches%20like%20I'd%20never%20had%20before.%20It%20was%20worse%20than%20giving%20birth.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJean-Claude%20Iribarren%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Airbus%20Atlantic%20works%20committee%2C%20said%20the%20food%20had%20been%20prepared%20by%20the%20company's%20canteen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''As%20we%20do%20every%20year%2C%20we%20organised%20a%20Christmas%20dinner%20for%202%2C600%20people%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20local%20suppliers.%20People%20have%20been%20a%20little%20hasty%20about%20the%20causes.%20We%20are%20obliged%20to%20keep%20samples%20of%20every%20product%20served%20in%20the%20restaurant.%20They%20will%20be%20analysed%20by%20the%20ARS%20%5Bhealth%20authorities%5D.%20The%20investigation%20will%20take%20several%20more%20days.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67808645%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Airbus%20Atlantic%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20aircraft%20maker%2C%20Airbus%2C%20and%20employs%2015%2C000%20people%20in%20five%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703511120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F12kg6cng_party_625x300_25_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F700-airbus-atlantic-employees-fall-sick-after-christmas-dinner-in-france-worse-than-giving-birth-4740320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Health%20officials%20are%20investigating%20whether%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20illness%20was%20a%20bacterium%20in%20the%20food%20or%20a%20very%20contagious%20gastroenteritis%20virus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F700-airbus-atlantic-employees-fall-sick-after-christmas-dinner-in-france-worse-than-giving-birth-4740320%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2F