2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fanger-in-poonch-after-videos-show-three-dead-after-alleged-army-questioning%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESafeer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20whose%20brother%20is%20a%20head%20constable%20in%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cvideo%20width%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%20controls%3D%5C%22controls%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Csource%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fshorts%2F-YflgHiF6dA%3Fsi%3D2ZAinWTKhWgtsAL3%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fvideo%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20third%2C%20who%20is%20wearing%20a%20red%20t-shirt%2C%20is%20Irfan%20Ahmad.%20He%20is%2016%20years%20old%20and%20among%20those%20admitted%20to%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddique%20said.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20whole%20incident%20has%20sent%20shock%20waves%20through%20the%20Gujjar-Bakarwal%20community%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20which%20already%20battles%20poverty%20and%20a%20crippling%20lack%20of%20rights%2C%20among%20other%20problems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPoonch%E2%80%99s%20Topa%20Peer%20village%20has%20been%20locked%20out%20of%20the%20world%2C%20virtually%20sealed%2C%20thick%20with%20military%20presence%2C%20and%20under%20an%20internet%20shutdown%20since%20the%20bodies%20of%20those%20who%20had%20allegedly%20been%20tortured%20by%20soldiers%20from%2048%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20their%20families.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarpanch%20Ahmed%20also%20claimed%20that%20villagers%20are%20unable%20to%20visit%20the%20three%20families%20in%20their%20hour%20of%20grief%20because%20the%20army%20has%20cordoned%20off%20their%20homes.%20He%20also%20confirmed%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20and%20heavy%20army%20presence%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWali%20Mohammed%2C%20father%20of%20deceased%20civilian%20Mohammed%20Shabbir%2C%20says%20he%20has%20been%20drifting%20in%20and%20out%20of%20consciousness%20since%20he%20saw%20his%20son%E2%