20Public%20Relations%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJKCDC_%2Fstatus%2F1738762558688075973%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20death%20of%20three%20civilians%20was%20reported%20yesterday%20in%20Baffliaz%20of%20Poonch%20District.%20The%20medico%20legal%20formalities%20were%20conducted%20and%20legal%20action%20in%20this%20matter%20has%20been%20initiated%20by%20the%20appropriate%20authority.%20Government%20has%20announced%20compensation%20for%20each%20of%20the%20deceased.%20Further%20Government%20also%20announced%20compassionate%20appointments%20to%20the%20next%20of%20kin%20of%20each%20deceased.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKillings%20condemned%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20asking%20for%20a%20transparent%20inquiry%20and%20punishment%20for%20any%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20seems%20pointless%20given%20how%20those%20who%20are%20found%20guilty%20are%20released%20scot-free%20without%20serving%20their%20punishment.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20way%20to%20remove%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-to-remove-dilli-ki-duri-and-dil-ki-duri-pm-modi-to-jammu-and-kashmir-leaders-101624545589901.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edil%20ki%20doori%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20Dilli%20se%20doori%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20National%20Conference%20leader%20Omar%20Abdullah%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20recent%20release%20of%20an%20Army%20captain%20convicted%20of%20killing%20three%20men%20in%20a%20staged%20gunfight%20in%20southern%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shopian%20district%20in%20July%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPDP%20leader%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20has%20also%20condemned%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20three%20men%20Poonch.%20%E2%80%9CHad%20this%20happened%20under%20any%20other%20government%2C%20the%20godi%20media%20would%20have%20raised%20questions%2