20to%20strip%20them%20naked%20and%20pour%20heaps%20of%20red%20chilli%20powder%20on%20their%20gashed%20and%20wounded%20bottoms.%20A%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20video%20was%20verified%2C%20another%20disturbing%20fact%20came%20to%20light.%20One%20of%20those%20innocent%20civilians%20was%20already%20dead%20while%20this%20act%20of%20violence%20was%20carried%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20deeply%20distressing%20question%20came%20to%20mind.%20Who%20would%20dare%20to%20shoot%20such%20a%20video%20under%20those%20circumstances%3F%20Certainly%20not%20a%20civilian.%20Clearly%20it%20was%20one%20of%20them.%20The%20video%20was%20deliberately%20leaked%20and%20disseminated%20with%20the%20diabolical%20intention%20of%20conveying%20a%20chilling%20message.%20By%20the%20very%20same%20persons%20whose%20unprecedented%20presence%20through%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20justified%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20securing%20our%20lives.%20This%20is%20the%20side%20of%20the%20story%20that%20the%20media%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20you%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shameful%20incident%20took%20place%20after%20five%20Army%20men%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20ambush%20by%20militants%20in%20Poonch.%20Its%20certainly%20not%20the%20first%20time%20in%20recent%20years%20that%20the%20Army%20has%20suffered%20huge%20casualties%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Pir%20Panchal%20area%20never%20gravitated%20towards%20militancy.%20The%20last%20two%20decades%20witnessed%20relative%20peace%20in%20the%20area%20where%20people%20have%20cooperated%20in%20every%20manner%20possible%20with%20the%20armed%20forces.%20For%20militancy%20to%20erupt%20here%20is%20a%20worrying%20sign.%20Notwithstanding%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20false%20claims%20that%20it%20has%20wiped%20out%20terrorism%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%20This%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20has%20now%20engulfed%20even%20a%20region%20like%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20which%20have%20remained%20peaceful%20even%20during%20peak%20insurgency%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-bjps-poison-has-now-reached-indias-schools%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Poison%20Has%20Now%20Reached%20India%E2%80%99s%20Schools%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20a%20retired%20SP%20was%20shot%20dead%20at%20a%20mosque%20in%20Baramulla%20despite%20a%20heavy%20security%20presence%2C%20The%20falsehood%20created%20and%20propagated%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20about%20Article%20370%20being%20responsible%20for%20unrest%20and%20violence%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20stands%20exposed.%20This%20is%20the%20argument%20that%20was%20invoked%20for%20their%20unconstitutional%20and%20illegal%20action%20of%20scrapping%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20special%20status.%20In%20doing%20so%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20desecrate%20our%20special%20constitution%20but%20also%20subverted%20the%20constitution%20of%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20offered%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20to%20undo%20this%20political%20%3Cem%3Eharakiri%3C%2Fem%3E%20ignored%20its%20own%20earlier%20decisions%20and%20went%20along%20with%20the%20majoritarian%20sentiment.%20To%20put%20facts%20into%20perspective%2C%20in%20cases%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F879068%2F%5C%22%3ESampat%20Prakash%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F153910827%2F%5C%22%3EVijay%20Lakshmi%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20the%20top%20court%20upheld%20that%20Article%20370%20though%20a%20temporary%20provision%20can%20be%20scrapped%20only%20with%20the%20recommendation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20constituent%20assembly%20to%20the%20president.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20no%20other%20institution%20including%20parliament%20had%20the%20right%20to%20tamper%20with%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20and%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20constitution%20is%20the%20supreme%20authority%20and%20cannot%20be%20overruled%20by%20a%20government%20that%20commands%20brute%20majority%20in%20the%20parliament.%20Even%20the%20apex%20court%20is%20bound%20to%20uphold%20its%20provisions.%20But%20when%20it%20came%20to%20Article%20370%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20constitution%20has%20been%20relegated%20to%20the%20corner.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20minorities%20are%20being%20reduced%20to%20second%20class%20citizens%2C%20as%20residents%20of%20the%20only%20Muslim%20majority%20state%20which%20has%20been%20dismembered%20and%20disempowered%20after%202019%2C%20it%20was%20natural%20for%20us%20to%20place%20some%20faith%20in%20the%20judiciary.%20Alas%2C%20even%20this%20glimmer%20of%20faith%20was%20misplaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20verdict%20was%20a%20test%20for%20the%20honourable%20institution%20to%20not%20only%20uphold%20its%20earlier%20judgements%20regarding%20J%26amp%3BK%20but%20also%20save%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20from%20being%20undermined%20even%20further.%20For%20those%20of%20us%20who%20believe%20and%20cherish%20the%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20Article%20370%20was%20like%20a%20bridge%20that%20connected%20us%20to%20the%20country.%20It%20had%20little%20importance%20for%20those%20who%20nurtured%20the%20sentiment%20of%20separatism.%20By%20doing%20away%20with%20it%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20obliterated%20the%20middle%20ground%20that%20pushed%20for%20democracy%20and%20peace%20with%20dignity.%20Instead%2C%20it%20has%20strengthened%20the%20narrative%20of%20separatists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjammu-kashmir-without-elected-government-five-years%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%3A%20In%205%20Years%20Without%20Elected%20Govt%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Crown%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20Has%20Become%20a%20Khap%20Panchayat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facade%20of%20normalcy%20continues%20to%20exact%20a%20heavy%20price%20from%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%20They%20have%20to%20pay%20with%20their%20lives%20and%20liberty%20to%20maintain%20a%20sullen%20silence.%20For%20the%20ruling%20government%2C%20the%20uptick%20in%20tourism%20has%20become%20a%20marker%20for%20its%20fake%20narrative%20of%20normalcy%20and%20is%20touted%20to%20strengthen%20its%20claim%20of%20establishing%20peace%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20a%20visiting%20tourist%20enjoys%20his%20short%20stay%20in%20the%20valley.%20Because%20unlike%20its%20inhabitants%2C%20he%20is%20not%20subjected%20to%20suspicion%2C%20religious%20prejudice%2C%20the%20threat%20of%20anti%20terror%20laws%20like%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA)%20and%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20(PSA).%20Nor%20does%20the%20sword%20of%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20or%20the%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20hang%20over%20their%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmiri%20youngsters%20are%20packed%20off%20to%20jails%20in%20and%20outside%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20trivial%20grounds.%20Businessmen%20and%20even%20small%20time%20entrepreneurs%20are%20raided%20day%20in%20and%20out%20just%20to%20instil%20fear%20within%20the%20community.%20Journalists%20whose%20duty%20is%20to%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%20are%20put%20behind%20bars%20for%20their%20reportage.%20Government%20employees%20are%20gagged%20through%20official%20orders%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20articulating%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20own%20admission%2C%20countless%20properties%20of%20common%20people%20too%20have%20been%20sealed%20without%20even%20giving%20them%20a%20chance%20to%20defend%20themselves.%20Even%20religious%20heads%20like%20%3Cem%3Emaulvis%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eimaams%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F936380%2Fin-kashmir-a-quiet-crackdown-on-mosques-and-clerics%5C%22%3Etold%20what%20to%20include%20in%20their%20weekly%20sermons%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20masses%20cannot%20protest%20peacefully%20even%20about%20day%20to%20day%20issues%20like%20gruelling%20power%20cuts%20that%20affect%20their%20lives.%20Even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmismatch-between-home-ministrys-report-on-jk-investments-and-its-statement-in-lok-sabha%2Farticle66334247.ece%5C%22%3EUnion%E2%80%99s%20claims%20about%20getting%20huge%20investment%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20patent%20lie.%20All%20major%20government%20recruitment%20schemes%20since%202019%20have%20been%20marred%20by%20scams%2C%20one%20after%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%20has%20changed%20after%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20it%20is%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20which%20was%20ahead%20of%20model%20states%20in%20terms%20of%20development%20indices%20is%20now%20lagging%20behind.%20There%20is%20growing%20unemployment%20(one%20of%20the%20highest%20rates%20in%20the%20country)%2C%20our%20local%20economy%20has%20been%20battered%20and%20even%20developmental%20contracts%20are%20being%20outsourced%20to%20outsiders%20who%20sublet%20it%20to%20locals%20after%20extorting%20a%20monumental%20commission.%20A%20beautiful%20prosperous%20state%20like%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20being%20torn%20apart%20psychologically%2C%20financially%20and%20socially.%20All%20this%20in%20the%20name%20of%20integrating%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfortunate%20fact%20is%20that%20this%20state%20and%20the%20pain%20inflicted%20on%20its%20people%20will%20always%20be%20used%20to%20earn%20votes%20throughout%20the%20country.%20Far%20from%20the%20show%20window%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawahar%20Lal%20Nehru%20promised%20to%20transform%20J%26amp%3BK%20into%2C%20it%20is%20now%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20ruin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMehbooba%20Mufti%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Democratic%20Party%20and%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20An%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20article%20made%20reference%20to%20a%20fourth%20civilian%20death%2C%20reports%20of%20which%20were%20unconfirmed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703427624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30123722%2FIllustration-Pariplab-Chakraborty.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-facade-of-normalcy-exacts-a-heavy-price-from-the-people-of-jammu-and-kashmir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kashmiri%20youngsters%20are%20packed%20off%20to%20jails%20in%20and%20outside%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20trivial%20grounds%20while%20the%20rest%20pay%20with%20their%20lives%20and%20liberty%20to%20maintain%20a%20sullen%20silence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-facade-of-normalcy-exacts-a-heavy-price-from-the-people-of-jammu-and-kashmir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Bethlehem%20is%20empty%20of%20joy%20-%20no%20Santa%2C%20no%20celebration'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703426694000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F10985%2Fproduction%2F_132137976_590243ec08d14153a47459de39b5b0e61b46aaae0_0_6720_44801000x667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67815370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20West%20Bank%20city%20of%20Bethlehem%2C%20usually%20bustling%20at%20this%20time%20of%20year%2C%20is%20subdued%20as%20war%20goes%20on%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1132%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67815370%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67815370.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67815370.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tanker%20Hit%20off%20Gujarat%20Coast%20by%20Drone%20Fired%20From%20Iran%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F17123254%2Fcontainer-ship-560789_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20According%20to%20the%20US%20military%2C%20a%20drone%20fired%20from%20Iran%20has%20hit%20a%20Japanese-owned%20chemical%20tanker%20located%20around%20370%20kilometres%20from%20the%20Indian%20coast%20off%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67811929%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20December%2024.%20Though%20the%20hit%20caused%20structural%20damage%2C%20no%20casualties%20have%20been%20reported%20and%20a%20fire%20aboard%20the%20tanker%20was%20put%20out.%20The%20Indian%20navy%20has%20sent%20an%20aircraft%20and%20warships%20for%20assistance%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BBC%20reported%20that%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20said%20that%20the%20tanker%20%E2%80%93%20named%20%E2%80%9CChem%20Pluto%E2%80%9D%2C%20donning%20a%20Liberian%20flag%20and%20operated%20by%20the%20Netherlands%20%E2%80%93%20was%20hit%20by%20%E2%80%9Ca%20one-way%20attack%20drone%20fired%20from%20Iran%E2%80%9D.%20The%20AFP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Ftanker-ship-off-india-hit-by-attack-drone-fired-from-iran-pentagon-says-%2F7410477.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20per%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20US%20military%20is%20in%20communication%20with%20the%20vessel%20%E2%80%9Cas%20it%20continues%20toward%20a%20destination%20in%20India%E2%80%9D%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20December%2023%20(06%3A00%20GMT)%2C%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukmto.org%2Findian-ocean%2Frecent-incidents%23%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUnited%20Kingdom%20Maritime%20Trade%20Operations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(UKMTO)%2C%20which%20provides%20information%20on%20maritime%20security%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20and%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%20The%20UKMTO%20reported%20that%20it%20received%20news%20of%20an%20attack%20%E2%80%9Capproximately%20200%20NM%20%5Bnautical%20miles%5D%20South%20West%20of%20Veraval%2C%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9Cauthorities%20are%20investigating%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20attack%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20drone%20and%20missile%20strikes%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67614911%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHouthi%20rebels%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20an%20Iran-backed%20group%20which%20controls%20a%20large%20part%20of%20Yemen%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20shipping%20route.%20According%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67614911%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBBC%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20attacks%20began%20after%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20with%20the%20Houthis%20declaring%20their%20support%20for%20Hamas.%20Their%20means%20of%20showing%20this%20support%20has%20been%20by%20attacking%20cargo%20and%20commercial%20vessels%20bound%20for%2C%20or%20linked%20to%2C%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20many%20shipping%20companies%20have%20stopped%20going%20via%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20choosing%20to%20reroute%20their%20vessels%20south%20of%20Africa%20despite%20the%20longer%20route%20and%20higher%20fuel%20costs.%20The%20US%2C%20along%20with%20more%20than%2020%20countries%2C%20has%20set%20up%20a%20multinational%20naval%20task%20force%20to%20protect%20ship%20movements%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Ftanker-ship-off-india-hit-by-attack-drone-fired-from-iran-pentagon-says-%2F7410477.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAFP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20US%20has%20openly%20accused%20Iran%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20support%20Hamas%2C%20of%20directly%20targeting%20ships%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%20Per%20the%20BBC%2C%20Iran%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20drone%20attack%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20vessel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0yet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20Israel%20had%20alleged%20that%20Yemen%E2%80%99s%20Houthi%20rebels%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20hijacking%20of%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-alleges-houthi-rebel-hand-behind-hijacking-of-india-bound-cargo-ship-in-red-sea%5C%22%3E%20Israeli-linked%20cargo%20ship%20headed%20from%20Turkey%20to%20India%20via%20the%20Red%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20hijacked%20vessel%20had%20been%20in%20Korfez%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Pipavav%2C%20India%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20seizure%20reported%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703422437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F17123254%2Fcontainer-ship-560789_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftanker-hit-off-gujarat-coast-by-drone-fired-from-iran-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20attack%20caused%20damages%20to%20the%20Japanese-owned%20ship%2C%20no%20casua