%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20if%20you%20end%20the%20negotiation%20in%20India%2C%20the%20conversation%20between%20the%20union%20India%20collapses%2C%20India%20tears%20itself%20apart.So%20you%20can%20see%20that%20Manipur%20is%20burning%2C%20you%20can%20see%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20burning.%20You%20can%20see%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20a%20problem.%20As%20somebody%20said%20to%20me%20the%20other%20day%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20problem%20on%20the%20edges.%20And%20if%20you%20want%20to%20understand%20a%20system%20you%20got%20to%20look%20at%20the%20edges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20scale%20civil%20war%E2%80%9D%20is%20underway%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20economic%20inequality%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20economic%20development%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmassively%20concentrating%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20talk%20about%20economic%20development%20you%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20question%20in%20whose%20interest%20is%20that%20economic%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRight%20next%20to%20the%20figure%20of%20growth%20in%20India%2C%20you%20have%20the%20figure%20of%20unemployment%20in%20India.%20So%20India%E2%80%99s%20growing%2C%20but%20the%20way%20it%E2%80%99s%20growing%20is%20by%20massively%20concentrating%20wealth%20towards%20very%20few%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEconomic%20growth%20without%20meaningful%20employment%20fosters%20inequality%20and%20undermines%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20only%20a%20few%20close%20wealthy%20fr