ellers%20have%20revised%20those%20figures%20down%20to%201%2C147%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20contrast%20in%20numbers%20does%20not%20diminish%20the%20losses%20or%20the%20tragic%20consequences%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side%20but%20the%20way%20in%20which%20revenge%20is%20being%20wreaked%20on%20the%20Gazans%20bears%20no%20comparison.%20The%20ignorant%20assume%20that%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war.%20Mainstream%20media%2C%20notably%20in%20the%20West%2C%20are%20getting%20the%20public%20to%20make-believe%20that%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0was%20the%20original%20day%20in%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20conflict.%20The%20fact%20is%20it%20happened%20in%20the%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20year%20after%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20May%2015%2C%201948%2C%20after%20Israel%20invaded%20Palestine%20and%20grabbed%20land%2C%20dispossessed%20the%20indigenous%20populations%2C%20imposed%20wars%20and%20key%20political%20raids%2C%20and%20kept%20stealing%20land%20after%20each%20occasion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20That%20catastrophe%20that%20beset%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20is%20generally%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Nakba.%20Whereas%2C%20the%20UN%20Partition%20agreement%20awarded%20the%20Arab%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estate%20a%20territory%20of%2011%2C100%20square%20kilometres%20or%2042%25%2C%20the%20Jewish%20state%20received%20an%20unjust%20proportion%20%E2%80%93%20a%20territory%20of%2014%2C100%20square%20kilometers%20or%2056%25.%20The%20remaining%202%25%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20the%20cities%20of%20Jerusalem%2C%20Bethlehem%20and%20the%20adjoining%20area%20%E2%80%93%20were%20to%20become%20an%20international%20zone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20naturally%20led%20to%20wars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fefraim-halevy-says-israel-guilty-of-seriously-underestimating-hamas%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Guilty%20of%20Seriously%20Underestimating%20Hamas%3B%20War%20Could%20Last%20For%20Years%3A%20Ex-Mossad%20Head%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReclaiming%20land%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20justice%20is%20justified%20even%20under%20international%20law.%20That%20is%20what%20Hamas%20set%20out%20to%20do.%20Today%2C%20Israel%20holds%20over%2078%25%20of%20what%20was%20once%20the%20entirety%20of%20historic%20Palestine.%20Some%20of%20those%20areas%20are%20now%20virtual%20Bantustans%E2%80%99.%20As%20a%20sealed-off%20enclave%2C%20fragmented%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territory%20(OPT)%20and%20controlled%20by%20Israel%20within%20its%20apartheid%20system%2C%20Gaza%20is%20a%20strip%20of%20land%20that%20can%20in%20many%20respects%20be%20likened%20to%20a%20Bantustan%2C%20when%20the%20indigenous%20people%20were%20shut%20off%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20population.%20The%20Separation%20Wall%20has%20created%20even%20more%20egregious%20apartheid-like%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fairly%20well%20guarded%20secret%20in%20neo-colonial%20circles%20that%20capturing%20Gaza%20is%20also%20about%20massive%20oil%20resources%20that%20the%20West%20wants%20to%20grab%20for%20its%20use.%20Israel%20plays%20the%20role%20of%20instrument%20in%20return%20for%20armaments%20to%20crush%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20Gaza%20that%20is%20under%20severe%20attack.%20Several%20cities%20and%20villages%20in%20The%20West%20Bank%20are%20also%20under%20constant%20threat%3A%20Jenin%2C%20Sheikh%20Jarrah%2C%20Nablus%2C%20Bethlehem%2C%20and%20several%20towns%20and%20cities%20places%20north%20of%20these%20areas%20with%20nightly%20attacks.%20The%20war%20is%20broadening%20and%20both%20sides%20are%20terrified%20of%20potential%20costs.%20Israel%20fears%20how%20Hamas%20is%20joined%20by%20Hezbollah%20and%20other%20resistance%20groups%2C%20even%20countries%20opposed%20to%20Israel%2C%20in%20the%20region.%20Yemen%20has%20hindered%20ships%20from%20and%20to%20Israel%20from%20using%20waters%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20costing%20Israel%20millions%20more%20to%20transport%20their%20goods.%20The%20need%20for%20a%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace%20is%20urgent%20because%20if%20the%20war%20to%20spread%2C%20it%20could%20only%20harm%20the%20entire%20global%20economy%20and%20global%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29164358%2FF_xf5OOXwAAsXcb-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDestroyed%20buildings%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20time%20to%20celebrate%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20what%20should%20Christmas%202023%20resemble%20for%20Christians%20and%20their%20churches%20in%20this%20context%3F%20The%20churches%20in%20Palestine%20are%20setting%20the%20tone.%20Christmas%20celebrations%20in%20Bethlehem%20have%20been%20cancelled.%20The%20Heads%20of%20Churches%20in%20The%20Holy%20Land%20have%20declared%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20celebrations%20for%20as%20long%20as%20the%20Israeli%20genocide%20of%20Palestinians%20is%20on.%20They%20now%20have%20to%20pick%20Christ%20from%20the%20rubble%20of%20the%20shattered%20homes%2C%20schools%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20other%20buildings%20that%20house%20vital%20project%20services.%20The%20Churches%20have%20asked%20that%20people%20stay%20in%20silence%20and%20pray%20for%20the%20victims%20and%20for%20peace.%20This%20should%20be%20a%20mandate%20for%20churches%20all%20over%20the%20world.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristians%20are%20now%20passing%20through%20the%20season%20of%20Advent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EAdvent%20is%20a%20season%20observed%20in%20most%20Christian%20denominations%20as%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20time%20of%20expectant%20waiting%20and%20preparation%20for%20both%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20Nativity%20of%20Christ%20at%20Christmas%20and%20the%20return%20of%20Christ%20at%20the%20Second%20Coming%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvent%20is%20the%20time%20to%20recall%20how%20god%20embraced%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20of%20people%20%E2%80%93%20the%20vulnerable%2C%20voiceless%2C%20poor%2C%20homeless%2C%20the%20marginalised%2C%20and%20the%20forgotten.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%202023%20is%20hardly%20the%20time%20to%20be%20celebrating%20when%20people%20in%20the%20entire%20Holy%20Land%20are%20suffering%20severe%20oppression.%20A%20relay%20of%20funerals%20is%20what%20one%20witnesses%20every%20day.%20If%20Christians%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20are%20planning%20celebrations%2C%20they%20must%20be%20conscious%20of%20the%20violence%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%20Just%20as%20Christ%20draws%20us%20to%20a%20journey%20where%20we%20shift%20from%20material%20celebration%20to%20those%20who%20are%20trampled%20over%20by%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful%2C%20the%20homeless%20and%20uninvited%2C%20the%20bombed%20and%20isolated%2C%20Christians%20are%20called%20to%20work%20for%20%E2%80%98peace%20on%20earth%E2%80%99%2C%20and%2C%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20notably%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChrist%20himself%20was%20born%20into%20the%20world%20unsolicited%20and%20as%20a%20source%20of%20annoyance%20to%20the%20ruling%20classes%20of%20those%20times.%20After%20finding%20no%20room%20to%20give%20birth%20to%20Jesus%2C%20Joseph%20and%20Mary%20who%20had%20traversed%20miles%20and%20miles%20upon%20a%20donkey%20where%20Mary%20could%20give%20birth%20to%20her%20baby%20found%20them%20rejected%20in%20place%20after%20place.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20night%20in%20Bethlehem%20is%20lived%20out%20today%20every%20day.%20This%20is%20the%20world%20at%20its%20worst%20regardless%20of%20where%20you%20are%20%E2%80%93%20Gaza%2C%20West%20Bank%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Tribals%20of%20India%2C%20Manipur%20in%20India%20and%20to%20the%20people%20in%20the%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98forever%20wars%E2%80%99%20in%20Africa%20as%20in%20Congo%2C%20Cameroon%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20Mali%2C%20Burkina%20Faso%2C%20South%20Sudan%2C%20and%20in%20Asia%20%E2%80%93%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20and%20West%20Papua.%20There%20is%20a%20colonial%20agenda%20behind%20each%20of%20these%20wars%20and%20they%20are%20about%20natural%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpeg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped-300x136.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07123715%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1024x464.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688063%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPeople%20search%20for%20their%20belongings%20in%20the%20rubble%20in%20the%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camp%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20UNRWA%2FAshraf%20Amra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20rubric%20of%20the%20expression%20%E2%80%98festive%20season%E2%80%99%2C%20commerce%20multiplies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ECorporate%20interests%20play%20up%20Christmas%20because%20it%20attracts%20consumer%20interests%2C%20which%20are%20a%20kind%20of%20opium%20that%20prevents%20working%20for%20real%20peace%20based%20on%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20world%20observes%20Christmas%20in%202023%2C%20the%20church%20must%20preach%20hope%20and%20justice%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20hate%2C%20and%20war.%20It%20must%20rebuff%20those%20who%20practice%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20ethnic%20superiority%20and%2C%20in%20its%20place%2C%20summon%20people%20to%20practice%20equity.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20genocide%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20wherever%20else%20there%20is%20oppression%20and%20cruelty%2C%20the%20church%20must%20practice%20the%20true%20meaning%20of%20Christmas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20true%20meaning%20of%20Christmas%20is%20found%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_American_Magazine%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20American%20Magazine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1889).%20I%20quote%3A%20Christmas%20calls%20on%20Christians%20%E2%80%9Cto%20give%20up%20one%E2%80%99s%20very%20self%20%E2%80%93%20to%20think%20only%20of%20others%20%E2%80%93%20how%20to%20bring%20the%20greatest%20happiness%20to%20others.%E2%80%9D%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20demands%20sacrifice.%20For%20Christ%E2%80%99s%20journey%20itself%20was%20a%20journey%20from%20%E2%80%98The%20manger%20to%20the%20Cross%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20thorny%20path%20in%20which%20he%20confronted%20the%20rich%2C%20powerful%2C%20and%20cruel.%20To%20claim%20Christmas%20as%20a%20festival%20of%20peace%2C%20love%2C%20and%20hope%2C%20is%20to%20engage%20in%20costly%20solidarity%20with%20the%20weak%20and%20powerless.%20Or%20else%2C%20we%20will%20be%20emptying%20Christmas%20from%20its%20very%20essence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%20this%20Christmas%20season%20be%20a%20time%20when%20humankind%2C%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20can%20aspire%20to%20a%20just%20world%20where%20death%20and%20destruction%20are%20left%20behind%20and%20an%20authentic%20peace%20be%20positioned%20through%20constant%20dialogue.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ERanjan%20Solomon%20is%20a%20political%20commentator%2Fhuman%20rights%20activist%2C%20and%20a%20long-time%20Palestine%20solidarity%20advocate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703414769000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F24161457%2FScreenshot-2023-12-24-at-4.09.24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fpalestine-genocide-christmas-israel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Christmas%202023%20is%20hardly%20the%20time%20to%20be%20celebrating%20when%20people%20in%20the%20entire%20Holy%20Land%20are%20suffering%20severe%20oppression.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fpalestine-genocide-christmas-israel%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Recipe%20for%20Change%3A%20Reshaping%20Our%20Food%20Systems%20Amid%20Rising%20Costs%20and%20Climate%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02214750%2Fimage-1468.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20shadows%20of%20climate%20catastrophe%20loom%20large%2C%20anxieties%20over%20rising%20temperatures%20and%20melting%20glaciers%20dominate%20the%20narrative.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20discussions%20about%20renewables%2C%20emissions%20reductions%2C%20and%20adaptation%20rightfully%20demand%20our%20attention%2C%20one%20vital%20dish%20remains%20tucked%20away%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20buffet%2C%20often%20under-seasoned%20and%20overlooked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20on%20the%2010%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20day%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20United%20Nations%20Climate%20Change%20Conference%20(COP%2028)%20that%20a%20crucial%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20climate%20change%20occurred%20with%20an%20urgent%20call%20to%20transform%20our%20global%20food%20and%20agriculture%20systems.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecognising%20the%20urgency%20of%20a%20sustainable%20and%20just%20food%20system%20transition%2C%20significant%20financial%20pledges%20were%20made%20to%20propel%20impactful%20actions%20forward.%20Multiple%20pavilions%20of%20global%20and%20national%20organisations%20showcased%20possible%20pathways%2C%20including%20India%E2%80%99s%20Community%20Managed%20Natural%20Farming%20initiative%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20The%20Agriculture%2C%20Food%20and%20Climate%20Action%20Toolkit%20was%20launched%20to%20assist%20countries%20in%20translating%20their%20commitments%20to%20actions.%20These%20are%20a%20few%20notable%20steps%20forward%2C%20among%20many%20more%2C%20that%20took%20place%20during%20the%20food%20day%20at%20COP%2028.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20weeks%20prior%20to%20COP%2028%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fao.org%2F3%2Fcc7724en%2Fonline%2Fcc7724en.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EState%20of%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Report%20(SOFA)%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rang%20alarm%20bells.%20Beyond%20concerns%20of%20hunger%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20or%20dwindling%20resources%2C%20a%20silent%20but%20insidious%20epidemic%20plague%20our%20food%20systems%20%E2%80%93%20hidden%20costs.%20These%20costs%2C%20encompassing%20environmental%2C%20social%2C%20and%20health%20downsides%20masked%20by%20low%20price%20tags%2C%20stand%20at%20a%20staggering%20%2410%20trillion%20annually.%20They%20are%20the%20polluted%20rivers%20choked%20by%20agricultural%20runoff%2C%20fertile%20soil%20eroded%20by%20chemical-intensive%20practices%2C%20and%20communities%20ravaged%20by%20climate%20shocks%20induced%20by%20our%20insatiable%20appetite%20for%20cheap%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fwhat-is-cop-and-why-should-i-care%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20COP%20and%20Why%20Should%20I%20Care%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20was%20a%20stark%20indictment%20of%20our%20current%20agricultural%20model.%20Beyond%20being%20a%20climate%20culprit%2C%20it%20stands%20as%20a%20chronic%20abuser%2C%20emitting%20a%20staggering%2024%25%20of%20global%20greenhouse%20gases%2C%20poisoning%20soil%20and%20waterways%2C%20and%20leaving%20millions%20vulnerable%20to%20food%20insecurity%20and%20malnutrition.%20This%20model%2C%20built%20on%20sand%2C%20is%20teetering%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20collapse%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20its%20own%20ecological%20transgressions.%20These%20environmental%20consequences%20translate%20into%20tangible%20threats%20such%20as%20droughts%2C%20floods%2C%20and%20a%20climate%20crisis%20threatening%20the%20very%20foundations%20of%20our%20food%20security.%20But%20the%20hidden%20costs%20extend%20far%20beyond%20environmental%20woes.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFarmers%2C%20the%20backbone%20of%20this%20system%2C%20often%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20its%20injustices.%20Trapped%20in%20a%20cycle%20of%20debt%20and%20low%20prices%2C%20they%20struggle%20to%20provide%20for%20their%20families%20while%20our%20plates%20overflow%20with%20cheap%20food.%20With%20rising%20food%20price%20inflation%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20households%20earning%20less%20than%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20find%20nutritious%20food%20unaffordable.%20This%20situation%20forces%20households%20satiate%20themselves%20with%20ultra-processed%2C%20least%20nutritious%20and%20cheap%20food%2C%20exacerbating%20their%20vulnerability%20to%20malnutrition%20and%20hunger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20food%20day%20at%20COP%2028%20and%20SOFA%202023%20shine%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20true%20price%20of%20our%20food%20choices.%20They%20force%20us%20to%20confront%20the%20social%20and%20environmental%20externalities%20baked%20into%20every%20bite%2C%20the%20costs%20shouldered%20by%20future%20generations%20and%20forgotten%20corners%20of%20the%20world.%20The%20clock%20is%20ticking%20on%20both%20our%20climate%20and%20our%20plates.%20Ignoring%20food%20system%20transformation%20is%20like%20trying%20to%20douse%20a%20raging%20inferno%20with%20a%20damp%20tea%20towel.%20We%20need%20a%20radical%20change%20in%20the%20recipe%2C%20a%20revolutionary%20shift%20from%20the%20current%20model%20to%20one%20that%20nourishes%20both%2C%20the%20people%20and%20the%20planet%20equally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20embark%20on%20this%20culinary%20revolution%2C%20we%20must%20demand%20six%20key%20ingredients%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEmbrace%20nature-based%20solutions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgro-ecology%2C%20regenerative%20agriculture%2C%20and%20ecosystem%20restoration%20are%20not%20fringe%20movements%20but%20the%20foundation%20of%20a%20resilient%20future.%20We%20need%20to%20ditch%20the%20chemical%20crutches%20and%20monoculture%20monotony%20for%20diverse%20landscapes%20teeming%20with%20life%20and%20productivity.%20Let%20us%20embrace%20agro-ecology%20%E2%80%93%20mimicking%20nature%E2%80%99s%20symphony%20of%20diverse%20crops%2C%20healthy%20soil%2C%20and%20symbiotic%20relationships%20between%20plants%20and%20animals.%20Regenerative%20agriculture%20adds%20a%20dash%20of%20carbon%20sequestration%2C%20building%20fertile%20soil%20that%20traps%20greenhouse%20gases%20and%20boosts%20climate%20resilience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPrioritise%20biodiversity%20and%20sustainable%20land%20management%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tapestry%20of%20life%20is%20not%20an%20ornament%2C%20but%20the%20very%20fabric%20of%20our%20food%20systems.%20Protecting%20and%20restoring%20biodiversity%2C%20from%20pollinators%20to%20soil%20microbes%2C%20is%20not%20a%20luxury.%20It%20is%20the%20bedrock%20of%20food%20security%20and%20ecosystem%20health.%20Biodiversity%20is%20not%20just%20a%20colourful%20garnish%3B%20it%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20pollinators%2C%20the%20nutrient%20cyclers%2C%20the%20natural%20pest%20control.%20We%20need%20to%20stop%20stripping%20the%20land%20bare%20and%20start%20protecting%20and%20restoring%20vital%20habitats.%20Agroforestry%2C%20organic%20farming%2C%20and%20ecosystem%20restoration%20must%20be%20the%20new%20culinary%20trends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24212038%2FIMG_2670.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24212038%2FIMG_2670.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24212038%2FIMG_2670-300x120.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24212038%2FIMG_2670-1024x410.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686289%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECultivate%20food%20system%20equity%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECheap%20food%20often%20comes%20at%20a%20hidden%20cost%20to%20farmers%2C%20communities%2C%20and%20the%20environment.%20We%20need%20to%20restructure%20food%20systems%20that%20empower%20farmers%2C%20prioritise%20fair%20prices%20and%20ensure%20access%20to%20nutritious%20food%20for%20all.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20an%20ethical%20imperative%2C%20it%20is%20a%20key%20ingredient%20for%20long-term%20stability%20and%20resilience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETransform%20food%20systems%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20about%20what%20we%20grow%2C%20but%20how%20we%20eat%20and%20waste.%20Let%20us%20reduce%20food%20waste%20and%20invest%20in%20efficient%20distribution%20systems.%20We%20need%20to%20ensure%20everyone%20has%20access%20to%20nutritious%20food%2C%20not%20just%20a%20privileged%20few.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIncorporate%20innovation%20and%20technology%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClimate-smart%20agriculture%2C%20sustainable%20packaging%2C%20and%20alternative%20protein%20sources%20offer%20promising%20solutions%20to%20reduce%20waste%2C%20optimise%20resource%20use%20and%20diversify%20our%20food%20options.%20But%20these%20tools%20cannot%20remain%20the%20exclusive%20domain%20of%20corporations%3B%20equitable%20access%20and%20knowledge%20sharing%20are%20crucial%20for%20widespread%20adoption%20and%20impact.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESupport%20collaboration%20and%20collective%20action%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20culinary%20revolution%20cannot%20be%20cooked%20in%20a%20one-person%20kitchen.%20We%20need%20a%20collaborative%20feast%2C%20with%20governments%2C%20NGOs%2C%20businesses%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20farmers%20all%20pulling%20up%20a%20chair%20at%20the%20table.%20Let%20this%20moment%20be%20a%20catalyst%20for%20multi-stakeholder%20partnerships%2C%20fostering%20knowledge%20exchange%20and%20joint%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20price%20of%20food%20is%20not%20what%20we%20pay%20at